## Currency Code Edge Cases

### Invalid currency codes (not 3 letters)
100 US
50 EURO
25 GB
1000 DOLLAR

### Currency code with lowercase
100 usd
50 eur

### Currency code with mixed case
100 Usd
50 eUr

### Currency code with numbers
100 US1
50 E2R

