## Multiplier Edge Cases

### Double multipliers
12kk meters
1MM kg
5BB feet

### Multiplier without number
k meters
M kg
B feet

### Multiplier in wrong position
meters 12k
kg 1M

### Invalid multiplier letters
12x meters
5y kg
10z feet

