## Complex Invalid Cases

### Multiple units
10 meters feet
5 kg pounds
100 miles km

### Unit + unit
meters feet
kg pounds

### Nested units
10 (meters)
5 [kg]

### Unit in wrong expression context
x = meters
y = kg 10
z = 5 + feet
